💻 PRINT LIBRARY IN C++
TO USE THIS SYNTAX OFF LIBRARY IS:

PRINT: print("hello worlds");
OUTPUT IN MACOS:
hello worlds%

OUTPUT IN WINDOWS:
hello worlds

PRINTLN: println("hello worlds")
OUTPUT IN MACOS:
hello worlds

OUTPUT IN WINDOWS:
hello worlds

HOW TO COMPILER IT

WHILE YOU USING CLANG:
clang++ main.cpp -lprint -o test;

WHILE YOU USING GCC:
gcc main.cpp -lprint -o test;


NOTE: IT CAN ONLY RUN ON MACOS; THERE IS NO VERSION FOR WINDOWS YET, SO IT CANNOT RUN ON WINDOWS!!!

